      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800235,
      "updated": 1772800235
    },
    {
      "id": "69aac8ea000000000024a879",
      "text": "         20 │   src: url(\"https://scrapbox.io/files/69903a273583dfb074cef65b.ttf\");",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800235,
      "updated": 1772800235
    },
    {
      "id": "69aac8ea000000000024a87a",
      "text": "            ╵            ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800235,
      "updated": 1772800235
    },
    {
      "id": "69aac8ea000000000024a87b",
      "text": "   ",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800235,
      "updated": 1772800235
    },
    {
      "id": "69aacb5d0000000000a9d4b0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800862,
      "updated": 1772800862
    },
    {
      "id": "69aacb830000000000a9d4c7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800901,
      "updated": 1772800901
    },
    {
      "id": "69aacb5d0000000000a9d4b1",
      "text": "from [Settings]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800862,
      "updated": 1772800862
    },
    {
      "id": "69aacb5d0000000000a9d4b2",
      "text": "Webフォント用CSS",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800862,
      "updated": 1772800862
    },
    {
      "id": "69aacb5d0000000000a9d4b3",
      "text": " [- bundleする時は、一旦これを一旦除外状態にしないとbundleに失敗します][Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800862,
      "updated": 1772800862
    },
    {
      "id": "69aacb5d0000000000a9d4b4",
      "text": " Google Fontsの日本語フォントのCSSは凄まじい文字数なのでbundleするのは無理なんだ。すまない…[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800862,
      "updated": 1772800862
    },
    {
      "id": "69aacb5d0000000000a9d4b5",
      "text": " あとscrapbox-bundler自体のバグなのか、`@font-face { src: url();}`内のバイナリファイルのURLにアクセスしようとしてbundleに失敗するんだ。変な[バグ]を踏んでしまい本当にすまない[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800862,
      "updated": 1772846000
    },
    {
      "id": "69aacb5d0000000000a9d4b6",
      "text": "  あーそれはパーセントエンコーディングかexternalの問題かも[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800862,
      "updated": 1772800862
    },
    {
      "id": "69aacb5d0000000000a9d4b7",
      "text": "  明日調べてみます",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800862,
      "updated": 1772800862
    },
    {
      "id": "69aacb5d0000000000a9d4b8",
      "text": "  お手数おかけします…[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800862,
      "updated": 1772800862
    },
    {
      "id": "69aacb5d0000000000a9d4b9",
      "text": "  一旦上のbundleのリンクのURL parametersのexternalにGoogle fontのドメインを足してみてください[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800862,
      "updated": 1772800862
    },
    {
      "id": "69aacb5d0000000000a9d4ba",
      "text": "   それで解決するかも",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800862,
      "updated": 1772800862
    },
    {
      "id": "69aacb5d0000000000a9d4bb",
      "text": "   書き方はすでに設定してあるexternalの記法を参照",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800862,
      "updated": 1772800862
    },
    {
      "id": "69aacb5d0000000000a9d4bc",
      "text": "   こちらでも試したいですが今スマホしかないのですまない",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800862,
      "updated": 1772800862
    },
    {
      "id": "69aacb5d0000000000a9d4bd",
      "text": "   ありがとうございます。externalにGoogle Fontsと`https://scrapbox.io/files/`を追加したところ、bundleが通りました[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800862,
      "updated": 1772800862
    },
    {
      "id": "69aacb5d0000000000a9d4be",
      "text": "   やはりそういうことか。解決してよかったです[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800862,
      "updated": 1772800862
    },
    {
      "id": "69aacb5d0000000000a9d4bf",
      "text": "   やったー！ダークになった！[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800862,
      "updated": 1772800862
    },
    {
      "id": "69aacb5d0000000000a9d4c0",
      "text": "   [https://gyazo.com/c726260726d79af801b62e001bd4f01a]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800862,
      "updated": 1772800862
    },
    {
      "id": "69aacb5d0000000000a9d4c1",
      "text": "   [Nrem.icon][***** 🎉]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800862,
      "updated": 1772800862
    },
    {
      "id": "69aacb5d0000000000a9d4c2",
      "text": "【問題が解決したため、ここにあった.cssは元のUserCSSに移しました】",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800862,
      "updated": 1772800862
    },
    {
      "id": "69aac8ea000000000024a87c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800235,
      "updated": 1772800235
    },
    {
      "id": "69aacb7c0000000000a9d4c6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800893,
      "updated": 1772800893
    },
    {
      "id": "69aacb790000000000a9d4c5",
      "text": "from [2026/02/14]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800890,
      "updated": 1772800890
    },
    {
      "id": "69aac97100000000007ee6b5",
      "text": "[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800370,
      "updated": 1772800373
    },
    {
      "id": "69aac97500000000007ee6b7",
      "text": "\t[scrapbox-bundler]直したいところがありまくりなのだが、だいぶコードがややこしくなっていて着手できていない",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800374,
      "updated": 1772800375
    },
    {
      "id": "69aac97600000000007ee6b8",
      "text": "  今ならcoding agentがあるから、開発再開できるかも",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800375,
      "updated": 1772800377
    },
    {
      "id": "69aac97200000000007ee6b6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800371,
      "updated": 1772800371
    },
    {
      "id": "69aac99b00000000007ee6c2",
      "text": "[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800413,
      "updated": 1772800416
    },
    {
      "id": "69aac99600000000007ee6b9",
      "text": " 井戸端を始動します",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800408,
      "updated": 1772800410
    },
    {
      "id": "69aac99600000000007ee6ba",
      "text": "　　第3、第4、第7井戸にいる従業員は、直ちに避難してください",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772800408,
      "updated": 1772800408
    },
    {
      "id": "69aac99600000000007ee6bb",
